# nvimclient
Open new file in existing neovim instance, worked on both windows and linux, powered by pynvim.

# Install
```bash
pip install nvimclient
```

# Usage
```bash
nvc foo.txt
nvc foo.txt -g # open in nvim-qt if not exist
```


